{
  "stem": "2718.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And this is a sad, sad story, that there were kapos here in Sydney who were kapos, and they were never, never exposed.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the result was that either people were, were lifting their legs fast enough, or they-- or they spilled the soup on themselves and they burned themselves.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They scalded themselves.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And it was not one case.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It was quite a few cases.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So after a while, people were just made to go and get the, the, the daily ration.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm not saying that it was only Jewish kapos.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were many kapos.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were kapos with green triangles who were murderers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were the kapos with red triangles who were political kapos.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But our people, they, they were unfortunately not much better.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So, so much for getting the food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] I just forgot what I wanted to say.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Is there another question?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Well, I was just going to ask you about being transferred to the labor camp in Germany.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when, when the time came, by that time when we went to-- when we knew that they were selecting people for a transport, the wor-- the worst thing one could do when it came to family-- father and son or any other relationship-- to try to stay together.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the minute they realized that, that, that it was a relationship, they went out-- they definitely went out of their way to separate the people, the family.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For what reason, we don't know, whether it was a sadistic reason or reasons-- this is how it was.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when-- somehow we knew when it was-- what sort of a selection it [INAUDIBLE] was-- health selection or a transport selection.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When it came to transport selection, we were standing apart from each other.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
